meouts, visual console\n• Great if you’re already deep on AWS\n• Fast for internal tools / moderate volume\n\nCons:\n• You don’t own the execution core — weak if workflow IS the product\n• Cost grows with many fine-grained state transitions\n• Lock-in; hard to self-host or go multi-cloud\n• Custom semantics (our error envelopes, resume UX, traces) get awkward\n\nUse when: internal tool + AWS-native stack.","fontSize":15,"fontFamily":5,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Pros:\n• Almost no custom orchestrator to build\n• Built-in retries, branching, timeouts, visual console\n• Great if you’re already deep on AWS\n• Fast for internal tools / moderate volume\n\nCons:\n• You don’t own the execution core — weak if workflow IS the product\n• Cost grows with many fine-grained state transitions\n• Lock-in; hard to self-host or go multi-cloud\n• Custom semantics (our error envelopes, resume UX, traces) get awkward\n\nUse when: internal tool + AWS-native stack.","autoResize":false,"lineHeight":1.25,"version":322,"index":"bI9"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"seed":35175424,"versionNonce":862862336,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1783935467642,"link":null,"locked":false,"type":"rectangle","id":"XE1U9ZIM7qYv9u7q6XvSj","x":-1996.219599435662,"y":1190.2496901427708,"width":220,"height":42,"strokeColor":"#7C3AED","backgroundColor":"#7C3AED","roundness":{"type":3},"version":322,"index":"bIA"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"seed":933313536,"versionNonce":575060992,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1783935467642,"link":null,"locked":false,"type":"text","id":"6Zmx15ArF5ZLUcOsNEud5","x":-1980.219599435662,"y":1198.2496901427708,"width":180,"height":22.5,"strokeColor":"#FFFFFF","backgroundColor":"transparent","roundness":null,"text"