rent","roundness":null,"text":"Core concepts:\n• Workflow — orchestration code (deterministic): what runs next, branches, waits\n• Activity — side effects: HTTP, Composio, sandboxed JS, DB writes\n• Worker — polls Temporal, runs workflows + activities\n• Event history — durable log; enables crash recovery via replay\n• Task queues — how work is routed to workers\n\nMental model: durable brain + history; your node executors become Activities.","fontSize":15,"fontFamily":5,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Core concepts:\n• Workflow — orchestration code (deterministic): what runs next, branches, waits\n• Activity — side effects: HTTP, Composio, sandboxed JS, DB writes\n• Worker — polls Temporal, runs workflows + activities\n• Event history — durable log; enables crash recovery via replay\n• Task queues — how work is routed to workers\n\nMental model: durable brain + history; your node executors become Activities.","autoResize":false,"lineHeight":1.25,"version":322,"index":"bIL"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":["IsD8lnHbcjxlOtNK9Poww"],"frameId":null,"seed":777960448,"versionNonce":997473280,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1783935467642,"link":null,"locked":false,"type":"ellipse","id":"jJUE8JFalc8Bo1fXVucZe","x":-1012.2195994356621,"y":1574.9996901427708,"width":40,"height":40,"strokeColor":"#22C55E","backgroundColor":"#22C55E","roundness":null,"version":322,"index":"bIM"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":["IsD8lnHbcjxlOtNK9Poww"],"frameId":null,"seed":1797733376,"versionNonce":965524480,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1783935467642,"link":null,"locked":false,"type":"text","id":"yOXCi2BmH6UoDjjDy7bsx","x":-1001.2195994356621,"y":1584.9996901427708,"width":160,"height":20,"strokeColor":"#FFFFFF","backgroundColor":"transparent","roundness":null,"text"